description.value:
The Living Quarters whilst aboard a Void Craft. Unpowered Decks, Cargo Holds, Bilge Berths. Neither safe nor pleasant, but at least you'll have stories to tell if you survive.

Requirements

Effect: Plentiful

Notes: 5 T
